item.description:
Join us this Sunday, Novemeber 18th, for another discussion of current topics.  There is no special topic planned at this point, but with the recent election, I'm sure we can come up with something.

A note for new people - the NuCafe has a full menu of breakfast and lunch items as well as a wide variety of coffees and teas.

Send an email or comment on this message if you have an item of particular interest

Please be prepared to contribute $3 towards the cost of the room.  Thanks
item.how_to_find_us: We'll be using the conference room
item.name: Sunday Morning Discussion
